Invocation Name: u. m. a. internet radio
des: Welcome to UMA Radio, the vibrant heartbeat of the University of Maine at Augusta! Our internet radio station is a dynamic and inclusive platform, proudly run by UMA students, staff, faculty, and members of our local communities statewide. We provide a diverse and eclectic mix of music, information, events and programming that reflects the unique spirit and interests of UMA and its locations statewide.
